      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just... watching a movie of myself. like i'm sitting in a dark room watching this person go through the motions of a life, talking to people, working, eating... but it isn't me. i've performed this role for so long that the real me is just gone. there's nothing left behind the mask.",
