      "role": "user",
      "content": "but letting go of the mask just feels impossible. like, if i actually stopped performing... if i stopped doing all the things the \"character\" in the movie is supposed to do... there'd just be nothing there. i'm scared that if i actually stopped, i'd just vanish. i don't think there's even a \"me\" to go back to.",
